Package business

Class UCDSystem

java.lang.Object
business.UCDSystem
All Implemented Interfaces:
Component
public class UCDSystem extends Object implements Component
UCD System represents the System Component of a Use Case Diagram. This class implements the Component interface and provides properties such as the name, position, wdith and height of the system. It also includes methods for displaying the use case and managing its properties and constraints.
